Add file /etc/apt/sources.list.d/dmx-repo.list
 * deb https://download.dmx.systems/repos/ubuntu/ xenial/

Add key:
 * curl -fsSL https://download.dmx.systems/repos/gpg | sudo apt-key add -
 
Install dmx:
 * sudo apt update && sudo apt install dmx

Known Issues:

 * After a fresh installation or update you need to restart dmx a few times before it comes up properly.


Juergen Neumann


